cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and word sense disambiguation. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel method for encoding word vector representations and extracting contextual words from text. Additionally, it may fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves analyzing text and retrieving relevant information. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society) as it deals with the societal impact of natural language processing and the need for accurate language understanding.
